I have had a lot of problems with being confident and making life seem worth it, I have really bad anxiety and depression, as a middle schooler that is not easy. Through out my surgery earlier this year and all of the hardships and different thoughts I have had about myself, being able to feel connect to someone through an art that doesn’t have any limitations or guidelines gives me a feeling that I don’t get anywhere else, you make all of it so fun and joyous for everyone who watches, and I don’t think you know how much you save people through your job, it is inspiring and so so fun to see how many techniques and perceptions there are to makeup. I don’t have any brand other than drug store, I spend my own money on makeup and enjoy every drop of it, but I have always made the best of what I have. Even with the makeup I have I would love to have a nibble of what you get to enjoy . When you announced your palette I was so excited, I wasn’t able to get my hands on it, but I made looks and recreated your art with the makeup I had. I hope you are so proud of every speck of glitter and pigmented shadow in that book. And I am so excited to see what is to come. I am not expecting you to see this, but it feels I have just gotten tons of weight taken of my shoulders. I would love to get some makeup, but what I wanted to get across here was the impact you make on the people that look forward to every upload and sentence that comes out of your mouth. Thank you so much Tati. I love you. 😘
